<Body><Title>四川汶川强地震近万人丧生 中国各界奋力救灾</Title>
	<ReportTime type="absTime">2008-5-13</ReportTime>
	<Content>
		<Paragraph>
			<Sentence><Event type="thoughtevent" eid="e1"><Participant sid="s1">中新社北京</Participant><Time tid="t1" type="relTime">五月十三日</Time><Denoter did="d1" type="statement">电</Denoter></Event></Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			综合消息(截至北京时间十时)
			<Event eid="e2"><Time type="absTime" tid="t2">北京时间五月十二日十四时二十八分</Time>，<Location lid="l2">四川汶川县</Location>发生七点八级<Denoter type="emergency" did="d2">地震</Denoter>。</Event>
			</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
			本次四川地震震级高，有感范围大，波及宁夏、甘肃、陕西、山西、山东、河南、湖北、湖南、重庆、贵州、云南、广西、西藏、江苏、辽宁、北京、上海等地。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

    强震造成近万人丧生 

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
			因此次四川地震震级高，又属浅源性地震，释放能量剧烈，给当地民众生命财产造成巨大的伤害和损失。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e3">据<Participant sid="s3">中国民政部</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d3">统计</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e4"><Time type="timeInterval" tid="t4">截至十三日九时</Time>，四川汶川县地震已造成<Location lid="l4">四川</Location>、<Location lid="l4">甘肃</Location>、<Location lid="l4">陕西</Location>、<Location lid="l4">重庆</Location>、<Location lid="l4">云南</Location>、<Location lid="l4">山西</Location>、<Location lid="l4">贵州</Location>、<Location lid="l4">湖北</Location>八省市共<Participant oid="o4">九千二百余人</Participant><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d4">死亡</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e5"><Denoter type="stateChange" did="d5">倒塌</Denoter><Object oid="o5">房屋五十余万间</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　决策层分层布置 确定救灾方针
    
　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e6"><Location lid="l6">汶川</Location><Denoter type="emergency" did="d6">地震</Denoter>发生后</Event>，
			<Event eid="e7"><Time type="relTime" tid="t7">五月十二日晚</Time>，<Participant sid="s7,s8">中共中央政治局</Participant>召开常委<Denoter type="operation" did="d7">会议</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e8">全面<Denoter type="operation" did="d8">部署</Denoter><Object oid="o8">当前抗震救灾工作</Object></Event>，
			<Event eid="e9">中共中央总书记<Participant sid="s9">胡锦涛</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d9">主持</Denoter><Object oid="o9,o10">会议</Object></Event>，
			<Event eid="e10">决定<Denoter type="operation" did="d10">成立</Denoter><Object oid="o10">抗震救灾总指挥部</Object></Event>，
			<Event eid="e11">由<Participant oid="o11">温家宝</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d11">任</Denoter>总指挥</Event>，
			<Event eid="e12"><Participant oid="o12" sid="s11">李克强</Participant>、<Participant oid="o12" sid="s12">回良玉</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d12">任</Denoter>副总指挥</Event>，
			<Event eid="e13">全面<Denoter type="operation" did="d13">负责</Denoter>当前的<Object oid="o13">抗震救灾工作</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
			会议要求，
			<Event eid="e14">要立即<Denoter type="operation" did="d14">组织</Denoter><Participant type="recipient" oid="o14" sid="s15,s16,s17,s18,s19">人民解放军</Participant>、<Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16,s17,s18,s19">武警部队</Participant>、<Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16,s17,s18,s19">民兵预备役</Participant>和<Participant oid="o14" sid="s15,s16,s18,s19">医疗卫生人员</Participant></Event>，
			<Event eid="e15">尽快<Denoter type="movement" did="d15">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l15">灾区</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e16">全力<Denoter type="operation" did="d16">抢救</Denoter><Participant oid="o16">受伤人员</Participant></Event>。
			<Event eid="e17">要千方百计向<Location lid="l17">灾区</Location><Denoter type="movement" did="d17">运送</Denoter><Object oid="o17">食品</Object>、<Object oid="o17">饮用水</Object>、<Object oid="o17">药品</Object>和<Object oid="o17">帐篷</Object>、<Object oid="o17">防寒衣被</Object>等救灾物资</Event>，确保灾区群众有饭吃、有衣穿、有干净水喝、有临时住处。</Sentence><Sentence>要迅速组织力量，
			<Event eid="e18">抓紧<Denoter type="operation" did="d18">抢修</Denoter>受损的<Object oid="o18">设施</Object>和<Object oid="o18">设备</Object></Event>，
			<Event eid="e19">尽快<Denoter type="stateChange" did="d19">恢复</Denoter>灾区的<Object oid="o19">通路</Object>、<Object oid="o19">通电</Object>、<Object oid="o19">通信</Object>和<Object oid="o19">供水</Object></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　解放军五万余人陆空开进灾区

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e20" type="thoughtevent">据<Participant sid="s20">中央电视台</Participant><Denoter type="statement" did="d20">报道</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e21"><Time type="relTime" tid="t21">目前</Time>，已有<Participant sid="s21">近两万解放军和武警官兵</Participant><Denoter type="movement" did="d21">到达</Denoter><Location lid="l21">灾区</Location></Event>
				<Event eid="e22">开展<Denoter type="operation" did="d22">救援</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e23">另有<Participant sid="s23">二点四万名官兵</Participant>紧急<Denoter type="movement" did="d23">空运</Denoter>到<Location lid="l23">重灾区</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e24">还有<Participant sid="s24,s25">一万名官兵</Participant>通过铁路输送<Denoter type="movement" did="d24">前往</Denoter><Location lid="l24">灾区</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e25">实施应急<Denoter type="operation" did="d25">救助</Denoter></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph> 

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e26"><Participant sid="s26">三千名公安消防和特警</Participant>也将紧急<Denoter type="movement" did="d26">调往</Denoter><Location lid="l26">灾区</Location></Event>。
		</Sentence>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e27"><Participant sid="s27,s28">中国国际救援队</Participant>也已<Denoter type="movement" did="d27">抵达</Denoter><Location lid="l27">灾区</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e28">开始<Denoter type="operation" did="d28">救援</Denoter></Event>。
		</Sentence>
		</Paragraph>

　　　有关部委迅速开展抗震救灾

　　<Paragraph>
			<Sentence>
				<Event eid="e29"><Location lid="l29">汶川</Location><Denoter type="emergency" did="d29">地震</Denoter>发生后</Event>，
			<Event eid="e30"><Participant sid="s30,s31">国家有关部门</Participant>立即<Denoter type="operation" did="d30">行动</Denoter>起来</Event>，
			<Event eid="e31">开展抗震救灾<Denoter type="operation" did="d31">工作</Denoter></Event>：</Sentence><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e32"><Participant sid="s32,s33">中国民政部</Participant>紧急<Denoter type="operation" did="d32"> 调拨</Denoter><Object oid="o32">五千顶帐篷</Object></Event>
				<Event eid="e33"><Denoter type="operation" did="d33">支援</Denoter><Location lid="l33">灾区</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e34">民政部长<Participant sid="s34,s35">李学举</Participant>亲<Denoter type="movement" did="d34">赴</Denoter><Location lid="l34">灾区</Location></Event>，
			<Event eid="e35"><Denoter type="operation" did="d35">协助指导</Denoter><Object oid="o35">抗震救灾工作</Object></Event>；</Sentence><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e36"><Participant sid="s36">卫生部</Participant><Denoter type="operation" did="d36">组织</Denoter><Object oid="o36" sid="s37">十余支卫生应急队伍</Object></Event>
				<Event eid="e37">已启程<Denoter type="movement" did="d37">赶赴</Denoter><Location lid="l37">灾区</Location></Event>；</Sentence><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e38"><Participant sid="s38">中国红十字会总会</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t38">十二日</Time>紧急向<Location lid="l38">灾区</Location><Denoter type="operation" did="d38">调拨</Denoter>五百余顶单帐篷、二千五百床棉被等价值七十八万余元人民币的<Object oid="o38">救灾物资</Object></Event>；</Sentence><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e39"><Participant sid="s39">全国总工会</Participant>向<Location lid="l39">灾区</Location>紧急<Denoter type="operation" did="d39">拨款</Denoter><Object oid="o39">一百万元救灾慰问金</Object></Event>，解决受灾职工生产生活困难……</Sentence></Paragraph> 

　　　国际社会密切关注表示关切

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>国际社会对四川汶川地震给予了极大关注，
			<Event eid="e40" type="thoughtevent"><Participant sid="s40,s41">多国政府首脑</Participant>纷纷<Denoter type="action" did="d40">致电</Denoter><Participant type="recipient" oid="o40">中国政府</Participant></Event>，
			<Event eid="e41">对<Object oid="o41">死难者</Object>表示了深切<Denoter type="action" did="d41">哀悼</Denoter></Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e42">联合国秘书长<Participant sid="s42,s43">潘基文</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t42">十二日晚</Time><Denoter type="action" did="d42">致电</Denoter>中国外交部长<Participant oid="o42">杨洁篪</Participant></Event>，
			<Event eid="e43">代表联合国向<Object oid="o43">中国地震死难者</Object>表沉痛<Denoter type="action" did="d43">哀悼</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e44" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter  type="perception" did="e44">表示</Denoter></Event>联合国将全力支持中国的救灾和重建工作。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e45" type="thoughtevent">美国总统<Participant sid="s45,s46">布什</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t45">十二日</Time>发表<Denoter  type="statement" did="d45">声明</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e46">向在四川地震中的<Object oid="o46">死难者</Object>表示沉痛<Denoter type="action" did="d46">哀悼</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e47">而<Participant sid="s47">美国</Participant>也准备好<Denoter type="operation" did="d47">协助</Denoter><Participant oid="o47">中国政府</Participant>救灾</Event>。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>
				<Event eid="e48">日本首<Participant sid="s48,s48,s50">相福田康夫</Participant><Time type="relTime" tid="t48">十二日晚</Time>通过中国驻日本大使馆<Denoter type="action" did="d48">致电</Denoter><Participant oid="o48">胡锦涛和温家宝</Participant></Event>，
			<Event eid="e49">向<Object oid="o49">地震灾区</Object>表示<Denoter type="operation" did="d49">慰问</Denoter></Event>，并
			<Event eid="e50" type="thoughtevent"><Denoter  type="perception" did="d50">表示</Denoter></Event>准备尽力提供所需援助。</Sentence></Paragraph>

　　<Paragraph><Sentence>此外，
			<Event eid="e51"><Participant sid="s51">海外华侨华人</Participant>已开始<Denoter type="operation" did="d51">捐款捐物</Denoter></Event>，
			<Event eid="e52"><Denoter  type="statement" did="d52">表示</Denoter>尽己之力，帮助灾区民众抗震救灾。</Event></Sentence></Paragraph>
	</Content>
